It seems that you have this line

Logger.addDataReceiver(WPILOGWriter())

in your Robot.kt during simulation.
Can you share the simulation log file? It should be under $PROJECT_FOLDER/logs/

Also, I have found a small mistake in your code, though it’s likely not the cause of the problem.
PivorIOSim.kt

inputs.relativePosition.mut_replace(sim.angleRads, Radians)
inputs.absolutePosition.mut_replace(sim.angleRads, Radians)

Not sure about Kotlin, but in Java, singleJointedArmSim.getAngleRads() returns the absolute position of the arm, but in the code, you used it for both the absolute and relative positions. So perhaps you want to fix that.
